{"type": "article", "id": 37838, "title": "还记得你玩的第一款电子游戏吗？这些盒子满满都是回忆｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-02-15T23:06:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 37680, "name": "Podo Labs"}, {"id": 37681, "name": "Kelly Behun"}, {"id": 37682, "name": "Paul Ketz"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170215220247bAePi20R57SDpjHz.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Glitch Artwork</h3><p>还记得吃豆人、超级马里奥、刺猬索尼克这些经典的电子游戏吗？为了表达对这些游戏幕后制作人员的敬意，来自加拿大的几位游戏爱好者创办了这个名为 Glitch Artwork 的手工品牌：他们用泡沫板制作一幕幕具有立体感的游戏场景，再加上黑色的展示盒。这些盒子看起来就像是将街机屏幕定格下来一样，相当复古。如果你想收藏这些盒子的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/GlitchArtwork\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价从 35 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220348c6w9GVTlSgeDjsrQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702152203488vdriuptszNGWMCj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220349e0SVOy58avKzYIFW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220349Gbn8tBNHzOiQmDK4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220348AcDgH2jie1P9pb8q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220349xAWMtGE6iKjzaFem.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Floor Pillows by Kelly Behun Studio</h3><p>天冷的时候，是不是看到厚实而且毛绒绒的枕头就很想把自己埋进去？美国纽约的设计师 <a href=\"http://www.kellybehun.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kelly Behun</a> 最近就推出了一套采用旧的摩洛哥纺织地毯制成的枕头，大胆的抽象图案加上丰富的配色让人眼前一亮，似乎连房间里的气氛都能变得活泼起来。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.1stdibs.com/dealers/kelly-behun-studio/furniture/more-furniture-collectibles/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 900 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220408oTAHlYQcGyJ6jIv4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017021522040826nHpMBKWrTya0V4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220408RB5Q4rlH1hiDxIE9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220408g02hJfpbwjB9WFCN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nest by Paul Ketz</h3><p>当其他设计师想着怎么帮助人们把东西收纳得更整洁时，来自德国的 <a href=\"http://www.paulketz.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paul Ketz</a> 琢磨着该如何让收纳变成一件好玩的事儿——坚信着 Humans love to play 的他，更希望自己的产品能够服务每个人内心深处那个爱玩的小孩。最近他推出了这款名为 Nest 的挂壁型收纳装置，金属框架当中是由橡皮筋构成的“网”，鼓励用户发挥自己的想象力打破传统的收纳模式，乱一点也没有关系。除了黑白两种款式之外，Ketz 还设计了西瓜配色，连皮筋末尾都特意染黑，就像是一粒粒西瓜籽。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.paulketz.com/buypaul/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1949 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220423mxLDRAjpX9lVafPB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220423cuUTw2A9mZ53eVLK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.627160\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220424fvpn5jdNMV7HWZzJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.565432\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220424b9epo3OjP4qhHRfX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.256250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702152204246dlA0LeMPovuxOh4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.287654\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Jack Adapter by Podo Labs</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.podolabs.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Podo Labs</a> 是一个来自美国洛杉矶的设计团队，让蓝牙产品更好用是他们主要的研发方向。他们最新的产品是一款名为 Jack 的蓝牙适配器，通过和其他音乐播放设备配对，它就可以让用户已有的耳机具备蓝牙功能，不用再额外购置蓝牙耳机。在市面上有不少同类产品的情况下，它还打出了共享音乐这一卖点：如果你和好友同时按下各自的适配器，就能听到同一首歌了。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/podolabs/make-any-headphones-wireless-jack-by-podo-labs\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 29 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702152204523cSMdTKnbIvsVFgC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.415625\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220451KXGDWHfeqBYbptzj.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.416667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220451uh6bxAsTS98cLP1l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.898529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220451yBcD6eibHApGuTOW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.138235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Walball</h3><p>为了缓解锻炼后肩背等部位出现的疼痛和肌肉紧绷的现象，来自美国的设计团队开发了一款名为 Walball 的便携式按摩球，帮助有健身习惯的人更好地放松。准确地说，它的外形更像是一个半球体的突起，底部的吸盘可以让它牢牢地吸附在墙面上，和需要自行移动或是固定的球体相比，能够更精准地定位到肌肉触发点。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1538614418/walball-the-ultimate-tool-for-fitness-work-and-tra\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 20 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220516MOh86JtaoQmjiVew.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220516m9aIUCbJXxcveWdn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220516M0s3JvqdwHuiR2fX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.445588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>AutoMed+ by Shima Jahani &amp; Ali Mahmoudi</h3><p>常见的药水包装总少不了用来服药的小量杯，这个看似便利的设计其实也有它的局限：对于有视力障碍或是手颤的患者来说，要准确地倒出剂量并不是件容易的事。为此，Shima Jahani 和 Ali Mahmoudi 两位设计师构思了一款名为 AutoMed+ 的概念药水瓶，瓶身配备了一个 LED 触摸屏，使用前只需要设置好服药频率和剂量，之后再摁下顶部的按钮，它就会自动倒出相应的剂量了。处于待机状态时，屏幕上还会显示当前所剩多少药剂，每服用一次底部就会多一条横线作为记录，忘记服药则会用空格表示。目前它还处于概念阶段。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220606eWcAdYLsgXQoSKxJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220606KMIq5N6mX3LtGpH2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220606lfjpLs9W3rSYik1q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170215220606hLyxYlTkzZXuHIbA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.811429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702152206067wIeP29y3YC0skpN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659048\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div>"}